thread.title: Migrant 'caravan' protests in Mexico after Trump tweets

title: Migrant 'caravan' protests in Mexico after Trump tweets
text:
Migrant 'caravan' protests in Mexico after Trump tweets Wednesday, April 04, 2018 - 01:38 
Migrants forming part of a dwindling group of largely Central Americans received transit visas to move through Mexico toward the U.S. despite tweets on the issue from President Donald Trump. No reporter narration.
